{"tid":1468643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（緊急）機場旅客屌到示威者喊！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T20:19:29.000Z","uid":91041,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c1f681dd2cfb6140f050ae544646689f855a4f19","tid":1468643,"uid":91041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:37:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今日所有check in counter 都close <br />\n但其實大部分航班根本就無取消！！<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日係機場好多旅客都以為flight cancelled <br />\n係機場入面好迷惘<br />\n<br />\n但<br />\n其實旅客係可以網上check in 攞boarding pass <br />\n直接係離境大堂好似平時scan boarding pass 過境走......？？？<br />\n入到禁區入面係有好多ground staff<br />\n問佢地 就知道應該點 仲應該上到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成件事好伏fake左好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人仲以為啲機真係cancel晒</span><br />\n<br />\n有無人講下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157765338794789&amp;id=725634788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157765338794789%26id%3D725634788&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=4221ddbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157765338794789&amp;id=725634788</a>"},{"pid":"2f900a1880831ae952fc7144c96aab5cb1b65e49","tid":1468643,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:40:17.000Z","msg":"咁係政府旗下嘅機場安排問題喎！煲大佢！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBczp5z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBczp5z.png&h=ef8f265e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.